full_text: ya his car- his driver actually took us - to Phantom. I didn't know any play could be so money. I had seen it before but still wilder 4 believe it. I believe it was fantastic. After the play we walked around the Plaza and went home. It was really fun. I met [DOJ REDACTION] and [DOJ REDACTION] they Mendison. he was different than I expected - pretty nice, but they didn't get along very well 4 at the big. when made me annoyed w/ him. he turned out to be pretty cool once he mellowed out. His brother Eric was 25 and we hung out w/ him a lot. The 4 of us went to their cabin. We had a lot of fun - X- rated stuff watched Sleuth [redacted] & hung out. See him again until Friday. We went to a club to watch some bands, to a bar
